Regression in Machine Learning:-  

This repository is dedicated to regression techniques in machine learning, which are used to predict continuous values and uncover relationships between variables.
Regression plays a crucial role in applications such as forecasting, trend analysis, and optimization.  

Contents:-  
- Algorithm Implementations:- Step-by-step code for Linear Regression, Polynomial Regression, Ridge, Lasso, ElasticNet, and more advanced methods like Decision Trees and Neural Networks for regression.  
- Use Cases:- Practical projects including house price prediction, stock market analysis, and sales forecasting.  
- Performance Metrics:- Tutorials on evaluating models using Mean Squared Error (MSE), R-squared, Mean Absolute Error (MAE), and other key metrics.  
- Data Handling:- Insights into preprocessing, feature scaling, and managing multicollinearity for better regression outcomes. 
